{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>救援人員到場進行搜索，政府飛行服務隊一度派出直升機到場協助搜救，暫時仍未見男子身影。救護車亦在場戒備。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127255529643970560174689.jpeg/pyOuyGasKdsjjuhZ8d0L0E_rWy5b4IJGsgnt35gJ7d8\" alt=\"消防員進行搜索。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>消防員進行搜索。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127255525038362624976048.jpeg/MU1BRBfjYFpJYXf4HAcgRGQ6sutk7cAADVSDzydUg88\" alt=\"救援人員到場進行搜索，救護車亦在場戒備。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>救援人員到場進行搜索，救護車亦在場戒備。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127255522836221952096751.jpeg/pXYN2OH1IY6fYWA18iT25DROydg5K7cokW4rFbtuKxU\" alt=\"救援人員到場進行搜索，救護車亦在場戒備。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>救援人員到場進行搜索，救護車亦在場戒備。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260502/1127255527328583680157639.jpeg/Sz23eYLAMeqqSYyCVEY0VrIIi2QqFf72EnWhEzh1oRM\" alt=\"男子電話訊號顯示在黃大仙沙田坳道法藏寺附近山坡。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>男子電話訊號顯示在黃大仙沙田坳道法藏寺附近山坡。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-02T06:55:21.858748+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":151,"images":4,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}